---
title: Buttons
---


<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h1>Overview</h1>
    <p>There are several button colors within Buoy. See <%= link_to "the UI Patterns section", sg_patterns_path %> for more information on how to use buttons within a design. All buttons share a class of <code>.Button</code>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Buttons</h2>
    <h3>Standard Buttons</h3>
    <div class="example ButtonGroup">
      <a class="Button">Default</a>
      <a class="Button Button--blue">Primary</a>
      <a class="Button Button--green">Creation</a>
      <a class="Button Button--red Button--outline">Destruction</a>
      <a class="Button is-disabled">Disabled</a>
    </div>
    <pre>
      <code><%= display_code('
<a class="Button">Default Button</a>
<a class="Button Button--blue">Blue Button</a>
<a class="Button Button--green">Green Button</a>
<a class="Button Button--red Button--outline">Red Button</a>
<a class="Button is-disabled">Disabled Button</a>') %></code>
    </pre>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns u-mb-5">
    <h3>Icon Buttons</h3>
    <p>Buttons with icons must include a class of <code>.Icon--{name of icon}</code>.</p>
  </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 columns">
        <div class="example">
          <a class="Button Button--icon Button--red Icon--close"></a>
          <a class="Button Button--icon Button--blue Icon--close"></a>
          <a class="Button Button--icon Button--green Icon--close"></a>
        </div>
        <pre>
          <code><%= display_code('
      <a class="Button Button--icon Button--red Icon--close"></a>
<a class="Button Button--icon Button--blue Icon--close"></a>
<a class="Button Button--icon Button--green Icon--close"></a>') %></code>
        </pre>
    </div>
  </div>  
</div>


<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns u-mb-5">
    <h3>Icon with Text Buttons</h3>
    <p>Buttons with icons and text must include both a class of <code>.Button--withIcon</code> and <code>.Icon--{name of icon}</code></p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 columns">
      <div class="example">
        <a class="Button Button--withIcon Button--green Icon--check">Much Success</a>
      </div>
      <pre>
        <code><%= display_code('
<a class="Button Button--withIcon Button--green Icon--check">Much Success</a>') %></code>
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns u-mb-5">
    <h3>Full Width Buttons</h3>
    <p>Full width buttons must contain a class of <code>.Button--fullWidth</code></p>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 columns">
      <div class="example">
        <a class="Button Button--blue Button--fullWidth">Full-Width Blue Button</a>
      </div>
      <pre>
        <code><%= display_code('
  <a class="Button Button--green Button--fullWidth">Full Green Button</a>') %></code>
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>